title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show MAR-11-2014 TUES
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show MAR-11-2014 TUES...PODCAST




The Glenn Beck Program



The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET



        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program - 3/11/14Tuesday, March 11, 2014 11:21 AM




   Buck is back in for Glenn and he breaks down the attack the left is waging
    on privilege and success with newly elected NY Mayor Bill DeBlasio's decision
      to close successful charter schools in NY. 

   Also, an update on what's happening in Ukraine and the threat from Russia.

       Plus, common core and the deterioration of education in America.
